<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Slightly Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 31 (Xinhua) -- The index of Tunis Stock Exchange
closed at 460.86 points on Monday, up 0.27 points from last Friday.
