<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 1 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index tumbled 110.58 points to close at
2,524.56.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching 52 trillion
Turkish liras (about 190 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down 108.90 points, or 2.77 percent,
to close at 3,122.33 points; the industrial index dived 128.54
points, or 5.40 percent, to close at 2,074.56 points; and the
service index tumbled 183.72 points, or 4.42 percent, to close at
3,294.83 points. 
</P>
