<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-President Meets St. Lucian Guests </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 1 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-President Hu
Jintao met here today with Mario Michel, first deputy leader of
