relief work.
</P>
<P>
Michel expressed sympathy for the serious floods now hitting
parts of China, and said he believes China will finally overcome
the difficulties brought on by the floods.
</P>
<P>
On relations between St. Lucia and China and the two
parties, Michel said St. Lucia-China relations have been
developing well even though the two nations forged diplomatic
ties only a year ago.
</P>
<P>
He said he hopes both sides will continue to make efforts to
deepen the friendly relations between the two countries and the
two parties. 
