<P>
The donated advertising time will be sold to domestic and
foreign corporations by the China Youth Development Foundation,
and the money gained will be used for school rebuilding in the
flooded areas along the Yangtze.
</P>
<P>
The China Youth Development Foundation enjoys a worldwide
reputation for "Hope Project" it initiated in 1989. The project
has already helped build 6,000 new primary schools in China's
poverty-stricken regions, bringing over 1.8 million dropouts back
to school in the past nine years.
</P>
